---
// Prime Citation — White-Label AEO for Agencies
// Built by an operator. Delivered invisible.

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="White-Label AEO Reports for Agencies"
  description="PrimeCitation delivers the foundational technical and entity work that modern search requires. Clean, unbranded reports and deployable assets under your brand."
>

<!-- ═══ NAV ═══ -->
<nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-charcoal-900/90 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="container-site flex items-center justify-between h-16">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-bronze-500">
        <path d="M3 16L9 4L15 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <path d="M9 4V20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-cream-50">PrimeCitation</span>
    </a>
    <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium">
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">How It Works</a>
      <a href="#for-agencies" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">For Agencies</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-bronze-500 text-cream-50 font-semibold hover:bg-bronze-400 transition-colors text-sm">Book a Strategy Call</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<header class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-bronze-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="container-site py-24 md:py-32 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.08]" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        Add a premium AEO layer to your existing client work<br />
        <span class="text-grad-bronze">without becoming an AEO specialist.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-stone-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        PrimeCitation delivers the foundational technical and entity work that modern search
        now requires. You get clean, unbranded reports and ready-to-deploy assets under your brand.
        Your clients receive sophisticated work. You protect and grow your existing relationships.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://checkout.stripe.com/c/pay/cs_live_a10GuCCp7E4bjaSCBjqUhUX5zlb3EiuaQOG2n3ZDt529QtJdVEN3gZt4ZH" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-lg bg-bronze-500 text-cream-50 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-bronze-400 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-bronze-500/20">
          Subscribe &mdash; $997/mo
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-600 text-stone-400 font-semibold hover:text-cream-50 hover:border-bronze-500 transition-all">
          See How It Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ═══ THE PROBLEM ═══ -->
<section class="container-site py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
      You know search is shifting.<br />
      <span class="text-grad-bronze">You're just not sure how to add AEO</span><br />
      without creating more problems than you solve.
    </h2>
    <div class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-[15px]">
      <p>Most established SEO agencies face the same situation:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 ml-0">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">&bull;</span> Clients are starting to ask about AI search and &ldquo;being cited by ChatGPT.&rdquo;</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">&bull;</span> You don&rsquo;t have the time or technical depth to become an AEO expert overnight.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">&bull;</span> Most AEO tools and services feel either too basic or too experimental to confidently put in front of long-term clients.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>So you do what feels responsible: you focus on the SEO work you already do well and wait for more clarity.</p>
      <p class="font-semibold text-stone-300">That caution is understandable. It&rsquo;s also starting to create a gap.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ THE SOLUTION ═══ -->
<section class="bg-navy-900/30 border-y border-white/5 py-20">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        A professional AEO layer<br />
        <span class="text-grad-bronze">that strengthens what you already sell.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-[15px]">
        <p>PrimeCitation was built for established SEO agencies that want to offer high-quality Answer Engine Optimization without turning their business model upside down.</p>
        <p>We handle the deep technical and entity work. You keep the client relationship and add your own strategic recommendations on top.</p>
        <p>Your clients receive a premium, white-label deliverable that feels like a natural extension of the work you already do for them.</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-stone-300">This isn&rsquo;t about replacing SEO. It&rsquo;s about adding the missing foundational layer that AI-driven search now demands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ HOW IT WORKS ═══ -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="container-site py-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
      Simple process. <span class="text-grad-bronze">Professional output.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-stone-400 mb-12 text-lg">Designed for agencies.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="card-surface flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-bronze-500/20 text-bronze-400 font-black text-lg mb-4">1</span>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2 text-cream-50">You send the website</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Share the domain of the client you want to support with AEO.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-surface flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-bronze-500/20 text-bronze-400 font-black text-lg mb-4">2</span>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2 text-cream-50">We deliver a complete package</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Clean, unbranded PDF report plus technical assets &mdash; optimized snippets, JSON-LD markup, entity strategy, and implementation guidance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-surface flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-bronze-500/20 text-bronze-400 font-black text-lg mb-4">3</span>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2 text-cream-50">You present it under your brand</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Add your own strategic recommendations and deliver it to your client. We stay invisible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-surface flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-bronze-500/20 text-bronze-400 font-black text-lg mb-4">4</span>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2 text-cream-50">We support the technical side</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">If questions come up or adjustments are needed, we&rsquo;re available behind the scenes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ WHAT YOU DELIVER ═══ -->
<section class="bg-navy-900/30 border-y border-white/5 py-20">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        <span class="text-grad-bronze">Not another surface-level audit.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-400 mb-10 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">PrimeCitation focuses on the foundational elements that determine whether a site can become a credible source in answer engines:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {[
          "Full site crawl with technical issue analysis",
          "Schema.org JSON-LD audit across all relevant entity types",
          "Entity coverage mapping (Organization, Person, Product, FAQ, LocalBusiness, etc.)",
          "Semantic HTML5 and heading structure review",
          "Core Web Vitals snapshot with targeted recommendations",
          "Content hierarchy and topical alignment analysis",
          "Competitive entity benchmarking against top competitors",
          "Ready-to-deploy JSON-LD markup and prioritized content briefs"
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-stone-400 p-4 card-surface">
            <span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5 font-bold">&#10003;</span>
            <span>{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-stone-500 text-center">You receive everything in one unified, professional document &mdash; ready for you to brand and present.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ WHY AGENCIES CHOOSE ═══ -->
<section id="for-agencies" class="container-site py-20">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center tracking-tight mb-6" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
      Quality you can stand behind.<br />
      <span class="text-grad-bronze">Margin you can actually keep.</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-[15px] text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p>We built PrimeCitation for agencies that care about the standard of work they put their name on. Every deliverable is created with the same level of rigor you apply to technical SEO and content strategy.</p>
      <p>Because we focus only on the foundational layer, you stay in control of the client relationship and the strategic recommendations. This keeps your margins strong and your positioning intact.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PRICING ═══ -->
<section id="pricing" class="bg-navy-900/30 border-y border-white/5 py-20">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center tracking-tight mb-10" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        Straightforward <span class="text-grad-bronze">pricing</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">
        <!-- Standard -->
        <div class="card-surface p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-cream-50 mb-2" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">PrimeCitation Professional</h3>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-cream-50">$1,197</span>
            <span class="text-stone-400"> /month</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-400 text-left">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Up to 5 white-label reports per month</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Full 8-dimension analysis on each site</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Clean, unbranded PDF + all deployable technical assets</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Behind-the-scenes technical support</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Founders Circle -->
        <div class="card-surface glow-bronze ring-1 ring-bronze-500/30 p-8 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-3 rounded-full bg-bronze-500/20 text-bronze-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Founders Circle</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-cream-50 mb-2" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">PrimeCitation Professional</h3>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-cream-50">$997</span>
            <span class="text-stone-400"> /month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-bronze-400 font-medium">Available for the first 15 agencies</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Locks in the $997 rate for the first 12 months</p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-400 text-left">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Everything in Professional, plus:</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Priority turnaround (24-48 hours)</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Direct access to the founder for strategy calls</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-bronze-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span> <span>Rate locked for 12 months</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://checkout.stripe.com/c/pay/cs_live_a10GuCCp7E4bjaSCBjqUhUX5zlb3EiuaQOG2n3ZDt529QtJdVEN3gZt4ZH" target="_blank" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-bronze-500 text-cream-50 font-bold text-sm hover:bg-bronze-400 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-bronze-500/20">
            Subscribe &mdash; $997/mo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Billing Example -->
      <div class="mt-10 card-surface p-6 max-w-lg mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-cream-50">Client billing example:</strong> Most agencies charge their clients between
          $1,800 and $3,000 per AEO project. With five clients, this creates
          <strong class="text-cream-50">$9,000 to $15,000</strong> in new monthly revenue against a $997 to $1,197 cost.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ TESTIMONIALS (PLACEHOLDER) ═══ -->
<section class="container-site py-20">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight mb-12" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
      Trusted by <span class="text-grad-bronze">Growing Agencies</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="card-surface p-10">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-bronze-500/30 mx-auto mb-6">
        <path d="M3 21C3 21 4 12 7 9.5C10 7 12 3 12 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M15 21C15 21 16 12 19 9.5C22 7 24 3 24 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      <p class="text-stone-400 italic leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        "PrimeCitation let us add a premium AEO layer to three existing clients in our first month. The reports are thorough enough that our clients think we built the capability in-house."
      </p>
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-charcoal-800 mx-auto mb-3"></div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-cream-50">Agency Partner</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Case study coming soon</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FAQ ═══ -->
<section id="faq" class="bg-navy-900/30 border-y border-white/5 py-20">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center tracking-tight mb-12" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        Common <span class="text-grad-bronze">Questions</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        {[
          ["Can I resell these reports under my own brand?", "Yes. PrimeCitation is explicitly designed for agency white-label use. The PDF ships clean with no PrimeCitation branding in the body. You add your strategic recommendations, bill your client at your own rate, and we remain your technical engine."],
          ["What does a full audit include?", "Every report includes: full site crawl with technical issue analysis, Schema.org JSON-LD audit across all relevant entity types, entity coverage mapping, semantic HTML5 and heading structure review, Core Web Vitals snapshot with targeted recommendations, content hierarchy and topical alignment analysis, competitive entity benchmarking against top competitors, and ready-to-deploy JSON-LD markup with prioritized content briefs."],
          ["What kind of agencies is this for?", "Established SEO and digital marketing agencies that want to add a high-quality AEO capability to their existing service offerings. You have existing clients you trust. We help you serve them at a higher level without hiring or disrupting your current operation."],
          ["How many reports can I get per month?", "Your subscription includes up to 5 full reports per month. Additional reports are available on request."],
          ["How does the white-label work?", "The PDF and all technical assets you receive carry no PrimeCitation branding. You can add your own logo, deliver them as-is, or enhance them with your own strategic recommendations. To your clients, the work appears to come entirely from your agency."],
          ["Is this replacing SEO?", "No. AEO is still a new channel and most of the signals overlap with what you already do. PrimeCitation focuses on the foundational entity and structured data layer that AI-driven search now surfaces. It strengthens and extends what you already deliver."]
        ].map(faq => (
          <details class="card-surface group">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-4 text-sm font-semibold text-cream-50">
              {faq[0]}
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-stone-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">{faq[1]}</div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FINAL CTA ═══ -->
<section id="contact" class="container-site py-20 md:py-28 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="card-surface p-10 glow-bronze">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
        Stop watching the shift.<br />
        <span class="text-grad-bronze">Start leading it for your clients.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-400 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        You don&rsquo;t need to become an AEO expert. You need access to one that meets
        the standard your clients expect from you. PrimeCitation gives you that access &mdash;
        white-labeled, professionally executed, and designed to complement the SEO work you already deliver.
      </p>
      <a href="https://checkout.stripe.com/c/pay/cs_live_a10GuCCp7E4bjaSCBjqUhUX5zlb3EiuaQOG2n3ZDt529QtJdVEN3gZt4ZH" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-lg bg-bronze-500 text-cream-50 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-bronze-400 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-bronze-500/20">
        Subscribe &mdash; $997/mo
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-stone-500">Limited spots available at Founders Circle pricing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ FOOTER ═══ -->
<footer class="border-t border-white/5 py-10 text-center text-xs text-stone-500">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-4 text-sm">
      <a href="/blog" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">Blog</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/StarbloomConsultingHub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://medium.com/@darrenkelly_90696" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">Medium</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/Starbloom_AI" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-cream-50 transition-colors">X</a>
    </div>
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} PrimeCitation. A Kelly Green Holdings company.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

</Layout>
